**Target:** Proposal for a regulation — Article 17 — paragraph 1 — point j

## Text proposed by the Commission

(j) the handling of communication with national competent authorities, competent authorities, including sectoral ones , providing or supporting the access to data, notified bodies, other operators, customers or other interested parties ;

(j)

(j)

## Amendment of the European Parliament

(j) the handling of communication with relevant competent authorities, including sectoral ones;

the handling of communication with national competent authorities, competent authorities, including sectoral ones , providing or supporting the access to data, notified bodies, other operators, customers or other interested parties ;

the handling of communication with relevant competent authorities, including sectoral ones;

